{
  "stem": "17761.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 103.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In June or July, 1944 we rented a train wagon-- two train wagons-- a number of families together, and we went to Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, under the rations we make-- could already make-- I told you-- I didn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I telled you, but-- I was working, for instance, in cutting tabak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used-- there was a man who had some funds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to buy leaves of tabak, and used to pay us some pennies to cut the tabak.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with that we made a living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe some of my little sisters worked something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We made, somehow-- I mean, we didn't go to [INAUDIBLE] Avenue for shopping, but we made, somehow, a living.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had some money that we could pay for renting the wagons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That is a story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know if you have time for that stories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we went, and we had to go to Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At the given point, these two wagons had to be detached from the train and connected to another train which went to Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they just forgot to do it, so we went-- we were attached to a train who went to the front, to Iasi-- next to Iasi.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we came to a place which is called, in Bessarabia, Belz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was a big station, so my father and another Jew from the other-- from the other wagon said, let's go here to the commander of the train station and we shall try to get us back, that we have to look on the front.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in Belz, we heard already the cannons from the front shooting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he went down, and as he went into the office, the train moved, and they remained there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we moved away.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
